                                        "Extraordinary"
                                    ], 
                                    "source": "Bestiary 2", 
                                    "text": "When a carrion golem is created, its creator infects it with a specific disease. The carrion golem can then infect those it strikes with its slams with this disease&mdash;most carrion golems inflict filth fever. The save DC is Constitution-based and includes a +2 racial bonus.", 
