                                    "text": "When a clockwork golem is reduced to 0 or fewer hit points, it explodes in a shower of razor-sharp gears and debris. All creatures within a 10-foot burst take 12d6 points of slashing damage&mdash;a DC 18 Reflex save results in half damage. The save DC is Constitution-based.", 
